Interface GiftCardHandlerInterface<T extends EFTResponse<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the EFTResponse Type
    public interface GiftCardHandlerInterface<T extends EFTResponse<T>>
    Implements this interface to allow handling of various gift card commands.

      • giftCardActivate

        EPSResult giftCardActivate​(EPSRequest request,
                           String posTransactionNumber)
        To activate pre-valued cards. Cards have a designated value in the bank's system and are shipped inactive. When the customer purchases the card, the activate transaction changes the status in the bank's database from inactive to active. This value is also used to activate new virtual gift cards.
        Parameters:
        request - the request
        posTransactionNumber - the posTransactionNumber
        Returns:
        EPSResult
